<style>
  :root {
    --color-bg-primary:#F8F9FA;
    --color-bg-header:#0A4A2F;
    --color-accent:#F28C38;
    --color-accent-hover:#E07B2D;
    --color-text-primary:#1A3C34;
    --color-text-secondary:#5C6B66;
    --color-text-muted:#8A9A94;
    --color-border:#E8F0EB;
    --font-heading:"Plus Jakarta Sans",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
    --font-body:"Inter",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
    --container:1200px;
    --radius-lg:1rem;
    --radius-xl:1.5rem;
  }
  *,::before,::after { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
  body { font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--color-text-primary); line-height:1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#fff; }
  .container { max-width:var(--container); margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }
  .container-narrow { max-width:780px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }

  .btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:.75rem 1.5rem; border:none; border-radius:999px; font-family:var(--font-heading); font-weight:700; font-size:.9rem; text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; white-space:nowrap; }
  .btn-primary { background:var(--color-accent); color:#fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:var(--color-accent-hover); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-secondary { background:transparent; color:#fff; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color:var(--color-accent); color:var(--color-accent); }
  .btn-outline { background:transparent; color:var(--color-text-primary); border:2px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:999px; }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color:#0A4A2F; color:#0A4A2F; }
  .btn-row { display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero-page { background:var(--color-bg-header); padding:5rem 0 4rem; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .hero-page::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 50%, rgba(242,140,56,.07) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events:none; }
  .eyebrow { display:inline-block; background:rgba(242,140,56,.15); color:var(--color-accent); border:1px solid rgba(242,140,56,.3); padding:.4rem 1rem; border-radius:999px; font-size:.75rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .hero-page h1 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.5rem); font-weight:800; color:#fff; line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:1.25rem; max-width:640px; letter-spacing:-.02em; }
  .hero-page h1 em { font-family:'Lora',serif; font-style:italic; font-weight:700; color:var(--color-accent); }
  .hero-page p { color:rgba(255,255,255,.7); font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.75; max-width:560px; margin-bottom:2rem; }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section { padding:5rem 0; }
  .section-alt { background:var(--color-bg-primary); }
  .section-eyebrow { font-size:.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--color-accent); margin-bottom:.6rem; font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .section-heading { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.5rem); font-weight:800; color:var(--color-text-primary); line-height:1.15; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-bottom:.75rem; }
  .section-intro { color:var(--color-text-secondary); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.7; max-width:600px; margin-bottom:3rem; }
  .section-header-center { text-align:center; margin-bottom:3rem; }
  .section-header-center .section-intro { margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; }

  /* ── SOURCING STATEMENT ── */
  .story-body { font-size:1rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.85; }
  .story-body p { margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
  .story-body p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
  .story-body strong { color:var(--color-text-primary); font-weight:600; }

  /* ── BRAND STATEMENT CALLOUT ── */
  .brand-statement { background:#F0F7F2; border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:2.5rem 3rem; margin:0; }
  .brand-statement h2 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--color-text-primary); margin-bottom:.75rem; letter-spacing:-.01em; }
  .brand-statement p { font-size:1rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.8; margin:0; }

  /* ── PRINCIPLE CARDS ── */
  .principles-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:1.25rem; }
  .principle-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:2rem; transition:all .3s; }
  .principle-card:hover { border-color:#0A4A2F; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(10,74,47,.1); transform:translateY(-3px); }
  .principle-card .icon { width:44px; height:44px; background:#F0F7F2; border-radius:.875rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .principle-card h3 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--color-text-primary); margin-bottom:.5rem; line-height:1.3; }
  .principle-card p { font-size:.875rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.65; margin:0; }

  /* ── CATEGORY CARDS ── */
  .category-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:1.25rem; }
  .category-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:2rem; transition:all .3s; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .category-card:hover { border-color:#0A4A2F; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(10,74,47,.1); transform:translateY(-3px); }
  .category-card.upcoming::after { content:'Coming soon'; position:absolute; top:1rem; right:1rem; background:rgba(242,140,56,.12); color:var(--color-accent); font-size:.65rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:.2rem .6rem; border-radius:999px; font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .category-card .icon { width:44px; height:44px; background:#F0F7F2; border-radius:.875rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .category-card h3 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--color-text-primary); margin-bottom:.5rem; line-height:1.3; }
  .category-card p { font-size:.875rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.65; margin:0; }

  /* ── FAQ ── */
  .faq-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:.75rem; }
  .faq-item { border:1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); overflow:hidden; background:#fff; transition:border-color .2s; }
  .faq-item.open { border-color:#c8dcc8; }
  .faq-q { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:1rem; padding:1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--font-heading); font-weight:700; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--color-text-primary); user-select:none; }
  .faq-icon { width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--color-bg-header); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
  .faq-icon svg { transition:transform .2s; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-icon svg { transform:rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-a { display:none; padding:0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); font-size:.9rem; line-height:1.75; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-a { display:block; }

  /* ── CTA STRIP ── */
  .cta-strip { background:var(--color-bg-header); padding:5rem 0; text-align:center; }
  .cta-strip h2 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight:800; color:#fff; margin-bottom:.5rem; letter-spacing:-.02em; }
  .cta-strip h2 em { font-family:'Lora',serif; font-style:italic; color:var(--color-accent); display:block; }
  .cta-strip p { color:rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size:.95rem; margin-bottom:2rem; max-width:520px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; line-height:1.7; }
  .cta-strip .btn-row { justify-content:center; }

  /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
  .breadcrumb-bar { background:#fff; border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .breadcrumb-bar .container { max-width:1100px; }
  .breadcrumb { padding:.6rem 0; font-size:.78rem; color:var(--color-text-muted); font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .breadcrumb a { color:var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration:none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color:var(--color-text-primary); }
  .breadcrumb span { margin:0 .4rem; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width:1024px) {
    .principles-grid, .category-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .hero-page { padding:3rem 0 2.5rem; }
    .principles-grid, .category-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .section { padding:3rem 0; }
    .brand-statement { padding:2rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width:480px) {
    .btn-row { flex-direction:column; }
    .cta-strip .btn-row { align-items:center; }
  }
</style>

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<div class="breadcrumb-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span>›</span>
      <span style="color:var(--color-text-primary);font-weight:600;">Sourcing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Section 1 — Hero -->
<section class="hero-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Sourcing</div>
    <h1>Freshness starts with <em>how we source</em></h1>
    <p>At GrowDirect, our sourcing approach is built around one core principle: freshness comes first. Our aim is to source as directly as possible from farmers and producers, building a food business shaped by real supply relationships, practical quality standards, and better value for modern households.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/pages/our-story">Our Story</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/collections/saver-boxes">Shop Saver Boxes</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2 — Main sourcing statement -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Our Approach</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">How GrowDirect approaches sourcing</h2>
    <div class="story-body">
      <p>GrowDirect is being built with a clear sourcing focus: wherever possible, we aim to source directly from farmers and producers. That approach helps us stay closer to the product, closer to quality, and closer to the standards we want customers to associate with GrowDirect.</p>
      <p><strong>Freshness is the blueprint behind the way we build our range.</strong> It is not just something we apply to fresh produce — it is the standard we want reflected across everything we source. As GrowDirect grows, that same fresh-first approach will continue to shape how we source across produce, pantry staples, and future categories including meat, seafood, and dairy.</p>
      <p>Our goal is to create a range that feels practical, trusted, and well chosen — built around real product quality, household value, and a simpler way to shop.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3 — Sourcing principles -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header-center">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Principles</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">What guides our sourcing</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">GrowDirect's sourcing model is shaped by a small number of principles that guide the products we bring into the range.</p>
