        </div>
        <h3>Farmer and producer focus</h3>
        <p>Our aim is to build direct sourcing relationships with farmers and producers wherever possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Practical household value</h3>
        <p>We source with everyday households in mind, balancing freshness, usefulness, and value.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>A better selected range</h3>
        <p>We want GrowDirect to feel considered and dependable, not overcrowded or confusing.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 4 — Current and future categories -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header-center">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The Range</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">What this means for our range</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">GrowDirect is beginning with a practical weekly shopping model and will continue expanding over time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="category-grid">

      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
