      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/><circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/><path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.61L23 6H6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Value-led household shopping</h3>
        <p>Our sourcing is shaped not only by product type, but by how real households buy — with a focus on freshness, simplicity, and everyday value.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="category-card upcoming">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Expanding categories</h3>
        <p>As GrowDirect grows, we plan to extend our fresh-first sourcing approach into future categories including meat, seafood, and dairy.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 5 — Brand statement -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="brand-statement">
      <div class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Our commitment</div>
      <h2>Built around freshness, not just supply</h2>
      <p>We believe sourcing should do more than fill shelves. It should shape the quality, consistency, and trust behind the full GrowDirect experience. That is why our focus remains on sourcing with freshness at the centre, and building the range from the ground up with care.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 6 — FAQ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;gap:4rem;align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <div class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Common sourcing questions</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7;">Questions about how GrowDirect thinks about sourcing and quality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">
            <span>Who does GrowDirect aim to source from?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">Wherever possible, GrowDirect aims to source directly from farmers and producers.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">
            <span>What is the main principle behind GrowDirect sourcing?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">Freshness is the core principle behind GrowDirect sourcing and the standard the business wants reflected across all sourced products.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">
            <span>Does sourcing only apply to fresh produce?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">No. While fresh produce is central to GrowDirect, the same fresh-first thinking is intended to guide pantry staples and future product categories as well.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">
            <span>Will GrowDirect add more categories in the future?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes. As the business grows, GrowDirect plans to introduce additional categories including meat, seafood, and dairy.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">
            <span>Why does GrowDirect focus on direct sourcing?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">Direct sourcing helps keep the business closer to quality, freshness, and the kinds of supplier relationships GrowDirect wants to build over time.</div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 7 — Closing CTA -->
<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Fresh-first sourcing, <em>built for modern households</em></h2>
    <p>GrowDirect is building a food business shaped by freshness, direct sourcing ambition, and practical weekly shopping for everyday households.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/pages/our-story" style="padding:1rem 2rem;">Our Story</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/pages/how-it-works" style="padding:1rem 2rem;">How It Works</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(function(q) {
    q.addEventListener('click', function() {
      var item = q.parentElement;
      var isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(function(i) { i.classList.remove('open'); });
      if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
    });
  });
</script>

